===Noun===
{{wikipedia}}
'''[[half]]-[[life]]''' (''plural'' '''half-lives''')

#{{physics}} The time required for half of the [[nucleus|nuclei]] in a [[sample]] of a specific [[isotope]] to undergo [[radioactive]] [[decay]].

